Package: homophily
Type: Package
Date: 2019-09-14
Title: Measuring Network Homophily
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Brendan", "Knapp", 
           email = "brendan.g.knapp@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3284-4972"))
Description: Homophily refers to the tendency of actors to share positive ties
    with other similar actors. The homphily package provides generic routines to
    measure this phenomenon on `<igraph>` and `<network>` objects.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.6)
